            <h3>Organization</h3>
            <p>Manage your organization details, branding, and contact information.</p>
            <button class="btn-secondary" disabled>Configure</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="settings-card">
            <div class="card-icon">üë§</div>
            <h3>Users & Roles</h3>
            <p>Invite team members and manage access permissions.</p>
            <button class="btn-secondary" disabled>Manage</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="settings-card">
            <div class="card-icon">üîî</div>
            <h3>Notifications</h3>
            <p>Configure email alerts and in-app notification preferences.</p>
            <button class="btn-secondary" disabled>Configure</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="settings-card">
            <div class="card-icon">üîó</div>
            <h3>Integrations</h3>
            <p>Connect with external services and data sources.</p>
            <button class="btn-secondary" disabled>View</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="settings-card">
            <div class="card-icon">üí≥</div>
            <h3>Billing</h3>
            <p>Manage your subscription and payment methods.</p>
            <button class="btn-secondary" disabled>Manage</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="settings-card">
            <div class="card-icon">üîí</div>
            <h3>Security</h3>
            <p>Password policies, two-factor authentication, and audit logs.</p>
            <button class="btn-secondary" disabled>Configure</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .settings-page {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .page-header {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    
    .page-title {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--growit-text);
        margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    }
    
    .page-subtitle {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--growit-text-muted);
        margin: 0;
    }
    
    .settings-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
    }
    
    .settings-card {
        background: var(--growit-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--growit-border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .settings-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--growit-text-dim);
    }
    
    .card-icon {
        font-size: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    
    .settings-card h3 {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--growit-text);
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    
    .settings-card p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--growit-text-muted);
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
        background: var(--growit-darker);
        border: 1px solid var(--growit-border);
        color: var(--growit-text);
        padding: 8px 16px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 500;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover:not(:disabled) {
        background: var(--growit-card-hover);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:disabled {
        opacity: 0.5;
        cursor: not-allowed;
    }
</style>
